#: ../../../system/qemu-colo.rst:326
msgid ""
"Note: If this Primary previously was a Secondary, then we need to insert the "
"filters before the filter-rewriter by using the \"\"insert\": \"before\", "
"\"position\": \"id=rew0\"\" Options. See below."
